node.text:
You become what you constantly feed your mind with.

If you constantly feed your mind with, “I can’t afford that, I can’t be rich, I can’t do that...”

Well guess what, you’re right.

Instead of telling yourself statements, which only closes the mind.

Change it to: “HOW can I afford that?”, “How can I be rich?”, “How can I do that?”. 

This will broaden your mind and you will start to think of solutions to your problem rather than excuses.

Did you find this helpful? Follow @savetoinvest for more!

#robertkiyosaki #moneymindset #richmindset #richmind #mindsetshift #changeyourmindset #savetoinvest
